title: ICYMI - Ana Navarro Talks Trump's Effect on the GOP & Florida's Heated Gubernatorial Race
itunes:title: ICYMI - Ana Navarro Talks Trump's Effect on the GOP & Florida's Heated Gubernatorial Race
description:
CNN political commentator Ana Navarro discusses how President Trump's divisive rhetoric and policies are redefining the GOP, then weighs in on Florida's 2018 race for governor.
